---
title: Roasted Sriracha Pork Belly & Egg Fried Rice with Creamy Slaw & Soy Garlic Greens
description: Zingy, sweet and packed with flavour, our sriracha is the perfect glaze for tender, slow-cooked pork belly. Freshen the dish up with crunchy cabbage, coated in a mayo and vinegar dressing and you're on your way to an unforgettable fusion dinner!
